<section id="about" class="about">
	<div class="container">
		<h2>About Us</h2>
		<div class="content">
			<div class="text">
				<p>The Lewis Paul Foundation is dedicated to raising awareness about sickle cell disease and supporting individuals and families affected by this condition. Our mission is to improve the quality of life for sickle cell warriors through education, advocacy, and community support.</p>
				
				<p>We work tirelessly to:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Provide educational resources about sickle cell disease</li>
					<li>Support research initiatives</li>
					<li>Offer assistance to affected families</li>
					<li>Create awareness in communities</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

